    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于模型失败，量化对冲基金在中国失去优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/quant-hedge-funds-are-losing-their-edge-in-china-as-models-fail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，在政府经济刺激计划的推动下，中国量化对冲基金的股价飙升，超出了其模型预期，并削减了空头仓位，这可能终结其多年跑赢大盘的记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/quant-hedge-funds-are-losing-their-edge-in-china-as-models-fail</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
